WEBVTT

00:08.109 --> 00:09.109
Drink.

00:09.110 --> 00:11.000
I'll ask you again.

00:11.283 --> 00:12.393
Lucien Grimaud,

00:14.200 --> 00:15.240
where is he?

00:18.330 --> 00:20.329
Bit sore, is it?

00:20.330 --> 00:23.098
Grimaud will finish the job soon enough.

00:23.330 --> 00:24.440
Your boss,

00:25.200 --> 00:26.240
the one who ran away,

00:26.555 --> 00:28.405
he's had his chance.

00:28.430 --> 00:30.230
He failed.

00:30.240 --> 00:31.330
Now it's our turn.

00:32.240 --> 00:33.420
We don't fail.

00:33.913 --> 00:36.853
Got to find him first, fat boy!

00:36.878 --> 00:39.156
Yeah, yeah. Yeah.

00:40.420 --> 00:42.210
Brujon, come here.

00:43.496 --> 00:44.523
Come here.

00:44.547 --> 00:46.547
- Whoa, whoa, whoa. No, no, no.
- Come here, come here.

00:48.260 --> 00:49.732
You want to be a Musketeer, don't you?

00:49.757 --> 00:51.340
He's a cadet.

00:51.654 --> 00:53.604
- I can't.
- It's fine, take this.

00:53.629 --> 00:55.669
Consider it an entrance test.
Take a big deep breath.

00:58.370 --> 00:59.390
Just relax.

01:05.665 --> 01:08.565
Shh, shh, shh... Easy, easy.

01:10.000 --> 01:16.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:18.570 --> 01:19.600
Fire.

01:19.610 --> 01:20.610
Wait!

01:24.170 --> 01:26.590
He left Paris last night.
I don't know where.

01:27.670 --> 01:29.520
- Fire.
- East!

01:30.214 --> 01:32.214
He rode east of the city.

01:32.239 --> 01:34.309
I swear I don't know any more.

01:36.400 --> 01:37.440
There we are.

01:38.550 --> 01:40.430
Thank you.

01:52.170 --> 01:53.545
You said he was a cadet.

01:53.570 --> 01:54.701
He is a cadet.

01:55.610 --> 01:57.470
He's a Musketeer cadet.

01:58.510 --> 02:00.817
You can go after him.
But you won't find him.

02:02.480 --> 02:04.760
And one night soon you'll wake

02:04.785 --> 02:06.964
and he'll be standing over your bed.

02:07.400 --> 02:09.509
And his face will be the last thing

02:09.520 --> 02:12.440
you see before you die.

02:38.857 --> 02:41.557
